23:13.183 --> 23:15.143
<i>So, what you gonna do with him?</i>

23:16.895 --> 23:19.231
<i>There's only one way this ends.</i>

23:51.930 --> 23:53.598
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

24:38.018 --> 24:40.228
<i>I can't do this.</i>

25:14.346 --> 25:15.889
<i>I hate to do this now,
