<i>Why did this happen?</i>

26:18.994 --> 26:21.454
<i>It's a senseless
act of violence.</i>

26:21.454 --> 26:22.914
<i>Was it?</i>

26:25.292 --> 26:28.253
<i>I know violence
is a part of this family.</i>

26:28.253 --> 26:31.590
<i>Carlo killed someone.
Mom, her family...</i>

26:31.590 --> 26:33.592
<i>I know what people
think about them.</i>

26:33.592 --> 26:35.343
<i>I-I've heard the stories.</i>

26:35.343 --> 26:38.096
<i>They can't all be lies.</i>

26:38.096 --> 26:41.266
<i>They revel in it.</i>

26:42.809 --> 26:44.728
<i>But we're not like them.</i>

26:44.728 --> 26:46.271
<i>Right?</i>

26:47.981 --> 26:51.026
<i>So, how do you do what they do?</i>

27:05.415 --> 27:08.168
<i>Yeah, we've been
waiting for you.</i>

27:10.754 --> 27:12.589
Little later than expected.

27:17.510 --> 27:19.346
<i>But I knew</i>

27:19.346 --> 27:22.098
<i>your old Al Capone-looking
ass was coming.</i>

27:24.225 --> 27:26.144
<i>Search his ass.</i>

27:27.354 --> 27:29.189
<i>My problem isn't with you.</i>

27:31.107 --> 27:32.734
<i>But you're in my neighborhood.</i>

27:32.734 --> 27:35.737
<i>If you knew I was coming
you know who I'm looking for.</i>

27:35.737 --> 27:37.405
<i>And if you knew
how thin my patience was</i>

27:37.405 --> 27:38.823
<i>you'd shut the fuck up.</i>

27:38.823 --> 27:41.660
<i>See, you thought
you was gonna come down here</i>

27:41.660 --> 27:45.580
<i>and bust some heads open,
and almost got your wig split.</i>

27:46.665 --> 27:49.417
<i>Lucky for you,
those weren't my orders.</i>

27:50.335 --> 27:51.419
<i>Yet.</i>

27:52.879 --> 27:55.298
<i>To have the audacity</i>

27:55.298 --> 27:57.676
<i>to roll up on that house</i>

27:57.676 --> 28:00.220
<i>after the shit
your daddy pulled...</i>

28:01.805 --> 28:04.349
<i>Tell me one thing.</i>

28:04.349 --> 28:08.520
<i>He don't know that
you here now, do he?</i>

28:11.272 --> 28:13.525
<i>If anything happens to me--
- If?</i>

28:15.485 --> 28:18.655
<i>If "if" was a fifth,
we'd all be fucking drunk.</i>

28:19.197 --> 28:21.950
<i>Do you know what
my family will do to you?</i>

28:21.950 --> 28:24.327
<i>Well, shouldn't matter
to you now.</i>

28:24.327 --> 28:26.579
<i>You'd be long gone by then.</i>

28:51.062 --> 28:52.480
We're on our way home.

28:52.480 --> 28:55.817
<i>You asked me
if I had control over my men.</i>

28:55.817 --> 28:56.985
<i>Now I'm wondering</i>

28:56.985 --> 28:59.028
<i>if you got control over yours.</i>

28:59.028 --> 29:00.739
<i>What is this?</i>

29:00.739 --> 29:03.158
<i>If someone were to come around
looking for trouble,</i>

29:03.158 --> 29:06.494
<i>I should assume
you sent them, yeah?</i>

29:11.124 --> 29:14.043
<i>I got your son.</i>

29:16.504 --> 29:17.922
<i>Is that so?</i>

29:17.922 --> 29:20.258
<i>Mm.</i>

29:21.050 --> 29:23.386
<i>Like I said before,</i>

29:23.386 --> 29:26.139
<i>young men are so impulsive.</i>

29:28.141 --> 29:30.852
<i>You tread very carefully
right now.</i>

29:30.852 --> 29:34.481
<i>Oh, if I wanted to kill him
he'd be dead.</i>

29:34.481 --> 29:37.567
<i>But he came to my house uninvited,</i>

29:37.567 --> 29:39.819
<i>swinging around his little dick.</i>

29:39.819 --> 29:43.406
<i>But given our situation,</i>

29:43.406 --> 29:45.867
<i>I'm willing to overlook all that</i>

29:45.867 --> 29:48.953
<i>to avoid a war
that neither of us need.</i>

29:49.454 --> 29:52.415
<i>And in case
I didn't make it clear,</i>

29:52.415 --> 29:54.793
<i>this is a courtesy call.</i>

29:54.793 --> 29:56.961
<i>You handle your boy,</i>

29:56.961 --> 29:59.506
<i>I'll handle mine.</i>

30:14.854 --> 30:16.272
<i>Time's up, Little Man.</i>

30:16.272 --> 30:18.149
<i>ominous music</i>

30:38.837 --> 30:41.297
Carlo.

31:10.159 --> 31:11.786
<i>Wait...</i>

31:22.755 --> 31:25.508
<i>Hi, Mr. Desiato.
I don't know</i>

31:25.508 --> 31:26.885
<i>if you remember me--
- I do.</i>

31:26.885 --> 31:29.429
<i>I remember you, Fia.</i>

31:31.890 --> 31:33.516
<i>Are you okay?</i>

31:41.190 --> 31:44.235
<i>I write to you every month.</i>

31:44.235 --> 31:46.529
<i>I know.</i>

31:46.529 --> 31:49.032
<i>I have some questions.</i>

31:53.453 --> 31:56.331
<i>Did Adam love me?</i>

32:09.052 --> 32:10.511
<i>I don't know.</i>

32:11.304 --> 32:13.890
<i>There was a lot</i>

32:13.890 --> 32:17.018
<i>that we didn't get a chance
to talk about.</i>

32:18.978 --> 32:21.272
<i>Well, he and I
became very close.</i>

32:21.272 --> 32:24.192
<i>Maybe we can fill in
some of the missing pieces--</i>

32:24.192 --> 32:26.569
<i>No. No.</i>

32:26.569 --> 32:29.280
<i>No. I...</i>

32:29.280 --> 32:32.158
<i>I-I won't be able to help you.</i>

32:32.158 --> 32:34.619
<i>Look, I don't know</i>

32:34.619 --> 32:36.746
<i>if what Adam and I had
was the real thing</i>

32:36.746 --> 32:41.000
<i>or if it just seems that way
now because...</i>

32:57.308 --> 33:00.603
<i>Adam was a terrible liar.</i>

33:03.481 --> 33:06.484
<i>He didn't have that gift.</i>

33:06.484 --> 33:08.903
<i>So, if he told you
that he loved you,</i>

33:08.903 --> 33:11.990
<i>then it was true.
Now, please...</i>

33:13.366 --> 33:15.493
<i>...please, just
stay away from me.</i>

33:15.493 --> 33:17.578
<i>Please, can--</i>

33:24.794 --> 33:26.671
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

33:40.518 --> 33:44.564
<i>Welcome, everybody, to
this year's annual prison rodeo!</i>

33:45.898 --> 33:47.692
<i>While y'all are
getting turned in,</i>

33:47.692 --> 33:49.193
<i>don't forget to visit
the concession stand</i>

33:49.193 --> 33:51.863
<i>and our three-dollar
pup-and-suds special.</i>

33:51.863 --> 33:54.032
<i>Cold beer and a nice hot dog.</i>

33:54.032 --> 33:55.533
<i>Get you started today.</i>

33:55.533 --> 33:59.537


33:59.537 --> 34:02.331
Whoa! [chortles]

34:02.331 --> 34:04.125
<i>No early parole for him.</i>

34:06.044 --> 34:08.671
<i>Inmates Morris, Waters,</i>

34:08.671 --> 34:12.425
<i>Jiménez and Desiato.</i>

34:17.180 --> 34:19.682
<i>And now the event
y'all been waiting for.</i>

34:19.682 --> 34:22.560
<i>Who's ready for convict poker?</i>

34:22.560 --> 34:24.395
Yeah!

34:36.199 --> 34:37.909
<i>suspenseful music</i>

35:04.519 --> 35:06.395
<i>What are you doing
at this table, Judge?</i>

35:06.395 --> 35:08.064
<i>Huh?</i>

35:08.064 --> 35:10.274
<i>I'm here because I'm trying
to raise enough money</i>

35:10.274 --> 35:12.568
<i>so that my family don't starve.</i>

35:14.237 --> 35:15.446
<i>Just deal the cards.</i>

35:15.446 --> 35:17.156
<i>You gonna get yourself killed.</i>

35:17.156 --> 35:20.785
<i>All four contestants will play
a friendly game of cards.</i>

35:20.785 --> 35:23.454
<i>Last man to remain in his seat
wins a cash prize.</i>

35:23.454 --> 35:24.789
<i>May sound easy.</i>

35:24.789 --> 35:26.374
<i>Keep in mind,
they'll be doing it</i>

35:26.374 --> 35:29.877
<i>in the presence of
a one-ton bull named Malachi.</i>

35:57.155 --> 36:01.284
<i>Well, looks like
Malachi's taking his time</i>

36:01.284 --> 36:03.494
<i>assessing the situation.</i>

36:06.622 --> 36:09.041
Oh!

36:11.836 --> 36:14.046
<i>Who's it gonna be, folks?</i>

36:17.425 --> 36:19.844
<i>atmospheric music</i>

36:19.844 --> 36:22.847


36:23.848 --> 36:25.683


36:35.401 --> 36:37.695
<i>That boy
was on the horns of a dilemma</i>

36:37.695 --> 36:39.363
<i>for a bit, there.</i>

36:40.072 --> 36:43.784
<i>And we'll get him out of there.
We'll take care of him.</i>

36:58.007 --> 37:01.427
<i>Hey! Hey!
-</i>

37:01.427 --> 37:03.512
<i>Hey, boy, hey. Hey. Come on.</i>

37:03.512 --> 37:04.847
<i>Hey!
-</i>

37:04.847 --> 37:06.015
<i>Aah!</i>

37:06.015 --> 37:07.433


37:25.952 --> 37:27.370
<i>You know what
the fucked-up thing is, Judge?</i>

37:27.370 --> 37:28.829
<i>intense music</i>

37:28.829 --> 37:30.915
<i>It's got nothing to do with us.</i>

37:30.915 --> 37:33.501
<i>The bull decides
who wins or loses.</i>

38:03.823 --> 38:06.117


38:12.164 --> 38:14.625
<i>Well, this looks like we</i>

38:14.625 --> 38:17.169
<i>got ourselves a winner, folks.</i>

38:17.169 --> 38:20.339
<i>How about that?</i>

38:34.729 --> 38:36.856
<i>Is there any word on the boy?</i>

38:38.107 --> 38:39.650
<i>No, not yet.</i>

38:39.650 --> 38:41.986
<i>Where's your sense of urgency?</i>

38:41.986 --> 38:44.071
<i>What would you have me do?
- How about</i>

38:44.071 --> 38:47.241
<i>we go back to the Lower Ninth
with more men</i>

38:47.241 --> 38:49.660
<i>and we go get
some goddamn answers!</i>

38:49.660 --> 38:52.663
<i>It's not a real plan, son.
It's barely even an idea.</i>

38:52.663 --> 38:54.457
<i>Dad, I--
- Think before you speak!</i>

38:54.457 --> 38:57.418
<i>Think before you act.</i>

38:57.418 --> 38:58.753
<i>Don't yell at him!</i>

38:58.753 --> 39:00.504
<i>He's trying
to protect this family.</i>

39:00.504 --> 39:03.799
<i>Look where it got him.
- Oh, so we do nothing?</i>

39:03.799 --> 39:05.134
<i>He was nearly killed.</i>

39:05.134 --> 39:07.470
<i>Doesn't that act
demand retaliation?</i>

39:07.470 --> 39:09.638
<i>That act was retaliation.</i>

39:18.481 --> 39:20.691
<i>Patience</i>

39:20.691 --> 39:23.235
<i>is not inaction.</i>

39:27.114 --> 39:30.910
<i>And violence is not
a demonstration of strength.</i>

40:26.841 --> 40:28.384
<i>Well, go on.</i>

40:32.680 --> 40:34.306
<i>There's an address in there.</i>

40:37.643 --> 40:40.104
<i>Stay gone, Little Man.</i>

41:07.673 --> 41:09.592
<i>Hey, yo, we here. Where you?</i>

41:09.592 --> 41:12.011
<i>We got a problem.</i>

41:13.012 --> 41:14.889
<i>Little Man got away.</i>

41:16.515 --> 41:18.434
<i>You got to be
fucking shitting me.</i>

41:20.144 --> 41:23.189
<i>I'm-a deal with you later.</i>

41:37.870 --> 41:39.622
<i>slow, ominous music</i>

42:00.768 --> 42:03.354
<i>This invitation
ain't include a plus-one.</i>

42:03.354 --> 42:07.858
<i>Sorry, but he outranks you
on this one.</i>

42:11.737 --> 42:15.115
<i>Adam Desiato was my godson.</i>

42:15.115 --> 42:17.618
<i>I want to be here
when Rudy brings in the killer.</i>

42:20.496 --> 42:22.206
<i>He in there?</i>

42:22.998 --> 42:24.625
<i>Yeah, he's gone.</i>

42:27.044 --> 42:29.463
<i>You told me
I was getting the shooter.</i>

42:30.047 --> 42:33.926
<i>You think I'm-a hand over
a young Black boy to the police?</i>

42:33.926 --> 42:37.346
<i>So, we're out of agenda items.</i>

42:40.140 --> 42:42.685
<i>I'm done here.
- That's fine,</i>

42:42.685 --> 42:45.771
<i>but you walking away don't
make our problems disappear.</i>

42:45.771 --> 42:48.107
<i>Our problems?</i>

42:48.107 --> 42:51.443
<i>Yeah. Our problems.</i>

42:51.443 --> 42:53.445
<i>I got Baxters
with itchy trigger fingers</i>

42:53.445 --> 42:56.198
<i>and NOPD on every goddamn block
of my neighborhood.</i>

42:56.198 --> 42:59.243
<i>And you, Mr. Figaro,</i>

42:59.243 --> 43:02.580
<i>you need voters to feel...</i>

43:02.580 --> 43:06.041
<i>safe when they go to cast
they votes next week, yeah?</i>

43:06.792 --> 43:09.086
Seems to me, every one

43:09.086 --> 43:11.422
<i>of our problems disappears</i>

43:11.422 --> 43:14.508
<i>if you hand over Eugene Jones.</i>

43:15.384 --> 43:18.095
<i>Am I not making myself clear?</i>

43:18.095 --> 43:19.930
<i>All we need is a solved crime.</i>

43:19.930 --> 43:24.101
<i>Rudy here finds another body,</i>

43:24.101 --> 43:27.688
<i>one that can't talk,
to stand in for my guy.</i>

43:27.688 --> 43:29.607
<i>What am I supposed to do--</i>

43:29.607 --> 43:33.110
<i>just find a random body
at the body store?</i>

43:33.110 --> 43:35.654
<i>Yeah. Ain't never
stopped y'all before.</i>

43:38.324 --> 43:41.201
<i>You declare the city safe.</i>

43:42.202 --> 43:43.579
<i>And I make for damn sure</i>

43:43.579 --> 43:46.165
<i>Eugene Jones is never
heard from again.</i>

43:49.001 --> 43:51.128
<i>Well, what do you say,
Detective?</i>

43:51.128 --> 43:53.380
<i>Want to solve
the case of the year?</i>

43:59.637 --> 44:01.138
<i>It's Eugene's.</i>

44:01.138 --> 44:02.598
<i>He'd have it on him.</i>

44:43.055 --> 44:46.600
<i>Well, if it's any consolation,
the bull was denied parole.</i>

44:54.233 --> 44:56.068
<i>I've secured your release.</i>

44:56.068 --> 44:57.861
<i>Yeah, well...</i>

44:57.861 --> 45:00.656
<i>I'm still not helping you
get Jimmy Baxter.</i>

45:00.656 --> 45:03.784
<i>I can understand
why you wouldn't do it for me.</i>

45:03.784 --> 45:06.453
<i>But I think you should do it
for Charlie Figaro.</i>

45:06.453 --> 45:08.455
<i>Why?</i>

45:08.455 --> 45:10.666
<i>Because he could
be in a lot of trouble.</i>

45:10.666 --> 45:12.918
<i>And if you help me,</i>

45:12.918 --> 45:15.587
<i>I can make his problems go away.</i>

45:16.171 --> 45:20.551
<i>I'm not doing anything for you
until I know why.</i>

45:26.265 --> 45:29.476
<i>How did you
get Kofi Jones to steal the car?</i>

45:29.476 --> 45:32.813
I called Charlie.

45:32.813 --> 45:34.314
Charlie Figaro?

45:34.314 --> 45:37.234
Yes.

45:37.234 --> 45:40.404
<i>I told him
I needed the car gone.</i>

45:41.947 --> 45:44.408
<i>And he took care of it.</i>

45:49.079 --> 45:50.914
<i>Now, I imagine</i>

45:50.914 --> 45:54.418
<i>if you had all your faculties
intact in that moment,</i>

45:54.418 --> 45:57.129
<i>you would have never
implicated your best friend.</i>

45:57.129 --> 46:00.132
<i>But this right here--</i>

46:00.132 --> 46:02.384
<i>this is the end of his career.</i>

46:02.384 --> 46:04.261
<i>This is prison time.</i>

46:06.221 --> 46:09.099
<i>He helped you
in your hour of need.</i>

46:14.772 --> 46:17.441
<i>He's 19.
That's the youngest I've got.</i>

46:18.025 --> 46:22.154
<i>We don't get a lot of children
that go unclaimed.</i>

46:23.405 --> 46:25.115
<i>They don't look anything alike.</i>

46:25.115 --> 46:27.284
<i>I don't control the inventory.</i>

46:29.495 --> 46:31.955
<i>But...</i>

46:31.955 --> 46:34.541
<i>he has gunshot wound
to the face ought to help.</i>

46:49.014 --> 46:51.475
<i>All right, Eugene.</i>

46:54.019 --> 46:56.480
<i>Okay. Thanks.</i>

46:58.232 --> 46:59.483
<i>Looks like his own people</i>

46:59.483 --> 47:01.693
<i>shot him in the head
down by the lake.</i>

47:03.362 --> 47:05.864
Now, for a lot of us,

47:05.864 --> 47:08.992
<i>the words "New Orleans"</i>

47:08.992 --> 47:11.161
<i>have always sounded like home.</i>

47:13.080 --> 47:15.958
<i>This city is one big family,</i>

47:15.958 --> 47:18.043
<i>and we take care of our own.</i>

47:18.043 --> 47:19.503
That's right.

47:19.503 --> 47:22.130
<i>Even when a-a brutal murder</i>

47:22.130 --> 47:24.091
<i>threatens to tear us apart,</i>

47:24.091 --> 47:26.468
<i>we finds a way to come together.</i>

47:26.468 --> 47:29.304
<i>Thanks to the tireless work</i>

47:29.304 --> 47:31.265
<i>of our police officers,</i>

47:31.265 --> 47:33.517
<i>and to the cooperation</i>

47:33.517 --> 47:36.270
<i>of decent and ordinary citizens,</i>

47:36.270 --> 47:38.939
<i>the perpetrator has been found</i>

47:38.939 --> 47:40.941
<i>and is no longer!</i>

47:42.192 --> 47:44.862
<i>I said, "No longer a threat!"</i>

47:44.862 --> 47:47.030
<i>If I am elected,</i>

47:47.030 --> 47:49.491
<i>I will dedicate my mayorship</i>

47:49.491 --> 47:52.995
<i>to the memory of my godson,
-</i>

47:52.995 --> 47:55.831
<i>Adam Desiato.</i>

47:55.831 --> 48:00.002
